[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]的'''MFi认证'''（"'''Made for iPhone/iPod/iPad'''"）是用于苹果[[iPod|iPod]]、[[iPad|iPad]]和[[iPhone|iPhone]]的硬件和软件[[外部设备|外部设备]]开发者的许可程序 。该名称原是'''Made for iPod'''的缩写。该认证涵盖各种设备连接器，包括耳机插孔、原{{tsl|en|Dock connector|dock连接器}}和新的[[Lightning接头|Lightning接头]]，以及[[AirPlay|AirPlay]]支持。加入MFi计划并通过认证测试的公司能在其产品包装上展示特定MFi相关标志，例如“Made for iPod”标志。

== Made for iPod ==
原Made for iPod于2005年1月11日在{{tsl|en|Macworld Expo}}推出，尽管在此之前的一些产品采用称为“Ready for iPod”的标签发布。<ref name="Horwitz">Jeremy Horwitz, [http://www.ilounge.com/index.php/articles/comments/made-for-ipod-central-information-hub/ "Made for iPod central information hub"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ilounge.com/index.php/articles/comments/made-for-ipod-central-information-hub/ |date=20201020082715 }}, iLounge, 30 January 2005</ref>据报道，当时苹果对所有带有该标志的产品收取10%的费用，报道称这是一笔“税”。<ref>Peter Rojas, [http://www.engadget.com/2005/03/18/apple-wants-a-10-cut-of-all-made-for-ipod-accessories/ "Apple wants a 10% cut of all Made for iPod accessories"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.engadget.com/2005/03/18/apple-wants-a-10-cut-of-all-made-for-ipod-accessories/ |date=20200114234345 }}, Engaget, 18 March 2005</ref><ref>Ina Fried, [http://news.cnet.com/Apple-seeks-tax-on-iPod-accessories/2100-1041_3-5620959.html "Apple seeks 'tax' on iPod accessories"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.cnet.com/Apple-seeks-tax-on-iPod-accessories/2100-1041_3-5620959.html |date=20141003152743 }}, ''cnet news'', 16 March 2005</ref> iPods使用一个扩展的[[TRS端子|TRS端子]]允许其他控制输入，例如静音和音量调整，并且许可证适用于插入插孔或坞站连接器的产品。<ref name="Horwitz">Jeremy Horwitz, [http://www.ilounge.com/index.php/articles/comments/made-for-ipod-central-information-hub/ "Made for iPod central information hub"], iLounge, 30 January 2005</ref>

当使用坞站连接器时，设备能够使用称为苹果配件协议（Apple Accessory Protocol，AAP）的简单串行协议控制iPod。这（正常情况下）使用19,200位/秒8N1通信信号发送包含命令的短分组，例如“录制语音备忘录”、“增加音量”。随着第三代iPod的推出，AAP也可用于耳机连接。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nuxx.net/wiki/Apple_Accessory_Protocol |title="Apple Accessory Protocol" |accessdate=2017-01-03 |archive-date=2019-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929051724/https://nuxx.net/wiki/Apple_Accessory_Protocol |dead-url=no }}</ref>许多Made for iPod设备还使用这些信号用于远程控制功能，包括汽车集成系统。

== 新的产品线 ==
[[File:Made_for_iPod,_iPhone,_iPad.png|thumb]]
随着iPhone的引入，计划名称扩展为“Made for iPod and Made for iPhone”，并且之后随[[iPad|iPad]]而变为“Made for iPod, iPhone and iPad”。该计划名称已正式更改为MFi，该术语在2010年左右曾被非正式使用一段时间。<ref>[http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20101202005137/en/GSLO-Pursues-Apple-License-Peel-520 "Company applies for Apple’s MFi Program"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20101202005137/en/GSLO-Pursues-Apple-License-Peel-520 |date=20190904171453 }}, BusinessWire</ref>

MFi计划现在也覆盖无限流式音乐的AirTunes系统。AirTunes最早于2004年在Mac和PC平台的[[iTunes|iTunes]]推出，<ref>[http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2004/06/07Apple-Unveils-AirPort-Express-for-Mac-PC-Users.html "Apple Unveils AirPort Express for Mac & PC Users"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2004/06/07Apple-Unveils-AirPort-Express-for-Mac-PC-Users.html |date=20170209041156 }}, Apple, 7 June 2004</ref>之后在被称为 [[AirPlay|AirPlay]] when 视频输出能力被添加到 [[Apple_TV|Apple TV]]等设备时。在iPhone和[[IPod_touch|iPod Touch]]具有Wi-Fi能力后，AirPlay进入设备。因为无须额外硬件，AirPlay已被官方和非MFi软件系统广泛实现（见[[AirPlay|AirPlay]]）。

== Lightning连接器 ==
随着[[Lightning接头|Lightning接头]]的出现，品牌被改变并官方成为MFi，这一术语在一段时间内被非官方使用。Lightning也引入了额外的协议，只有通过MFi认证才能取得官方支持。除了技术要求，根据TUAW，苹果还借此机会更新许可协议，要求所有第三方同意苹果的供应商责任代码。<ref>Michael Rose, [http://www.tuaw.com/2012/11/08/made-for-iphone-manufacturers-may-have-to-comply-with-apples-su/ "Made For iPhone manufacturers may have to comply with Apple's supplier responsibility code"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tuaw.com/2012/11/08/made-for-iphone-manufacturers-may-have-to-comply-with-apples-su/ |date=20150216032158 }}, ''TUAW'', 8 November 2012</ref>

== iOS 7及更高版本 ==
随着2013年[[苹果全球开发者大会|苹果全球开发者大会]]（WWDC）发布[[iOS|iOS]] 7开发者版本，新的MFi审批包括[[游戏控制器|游戏控制器]]，无论是夹在iOS设备上的环绕设计，还是完全独立的无线模型。<ref>Eli Hodapp, [http://toucharcade.com/2013/06/10/wwdc-2013-more-details-emerge-on-official-ios-game-controllers/ "WWDC 2013: More Details Emerge on Official iOS Game Controllers"] {{Wayback|url=http://toucharcade.com/2013/06/10/wwdc-2013-more-details-emerge-on-official-ios-game-controllers/ |date=20201112015539 }}, ''toucharcade'', 10 June 2013</ref>

希望将设备和应用程序与[[IOS_8|HomeKit]]集成的开发者必须成为MFi计划的成员，这样才能取得规范以及认证其产品。<ref>Lou Hattersley, [http://www.macworld.co.uk/feature/apple/apple-homekit-release-date-rumours-3585269/ "Apple HomeKit release date rumours: Apple's system for controlling gadgets in your home coming this spring"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.macworld.co.uk/feature/apple/apple-homekit-release-date-rumours-3585269/ |date=20170202162716 }}, ''MacWorld'', 28 January 2015</ref>

